{"tid":1245143,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"勁多分化post, 你地中晒計","createTime":"2019-06-20T07:47:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T09:01:18.000Z","uid":59618,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0d634203e9021abb250816ce585df7da8b58979e","tid":1245143,"uid":59618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T07:47:17.000Z","msg":"唔好同我講衝一個冇人既立法會或政總冇意思。<br />\n<br />\nApple都幫晒我地宣傳，有晒deadline, 有晒目標點解我地要衝，我地既訴求佢冇達到就已經係原因。<br />\n<br />\n再者，人地根本唸住消磨我地意志。一話唔開會就已經玩殘我地？你唸下21號唔出，佢下星期話重開會。會唔會再有人宣傳，會唔會再有咁多人？答案係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">冇</span></span><br />\n<br />\n以我睇法，今次一定係要訓身搞文宣，因為氣勢已經冇左一半，政府就係睇中呢點玩長久戰，你地唔係咁都唔明呀嘛？<br />\n<br />\n同埋，出黎坐係完全冇意思，200萬加一人都唔驚，驚你地幾萬人21號出黎坐？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你地中晒計</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3毛走開唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60fabb5192a8b046b83be9263db825a9d0c382c5","tid":1245143,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T07:49:41.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n唔好中計"},{"pid":"00ddd11c721e91407df97c0ba5917d21786724dc","tid":1245143,"uid":59618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T07:50:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cba0bcc5721a74088b64e4c2c1eb10ce6d8dd3fa","tid":1245143,"uid":161626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T07:50:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">[全力推] 621 CONTENT PAGE 唔好再俾膠鋪上熱門！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1245051\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1245051</a></span></span>"},{"pid":"597628afc5b8a9864aca6a3984c583e8ec3bbc08","tid":1245143,"uid":262482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T07:51:19.000Z","msg":"唔好中計"},{"pid":"9f5f65e767a351fa0dc9f9e03c5aa575e210b638","tid":1245143,"uid":240178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T07:52:52.000Z